    {
      "id": "1904750c-f3ba-808c-91ae-f1b619b929ea",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors evaluate student knowledge states in 2 courses from Arizona University using ALEKS. The authors look at unsupervised approaches and social network analysis to create embedding representations.",
